{"lemma":"حِزْبَيْ","slug":"حِزْبَيْ","root":"ح.ز.ب","root_slug":"ح-ز-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-ز-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"حِزْب","root":"حزب","pos":"N","occurrence_count":20},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":11},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n7826","n7829","n7830"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%90%D8%B2%D9%92%D8%A8%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"political party"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"team, group"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"collective, association"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"troop, number of men"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"confederates"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"partisans"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"sect"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"part"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"division of the Qur'an, hizb (one of the sixty sections into which the Qur'an is divided)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to befall, happen to, occur","tags":["ambitransitive"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of حَزَبَ (ḥazaba) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Probably together with Ge'ez ሕዝብ (ḥəzb, “people, nation”) borrowed from Old South Arabian 𐩢𐩸𐩨 (ḥzb, “troop”), originating there with assimilated voicedness from the verb cognate to حَسَبَ (ḥasaba, “to enumerate, to reckon”) in the understanding of “an enumeration (of men), a collective, a troop”.\n\nFrom the concept of exterior bands (أَحْزَاب (ʔaḥzāb)) pressuring upon a region."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n7826","headword_ar":"حزّب","root":"Hzb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (A, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taHoziybN","text_ar":"تَحْزِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He collected, congregated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"assembled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"people: (TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he collected,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"formed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"people"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"into"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHozaAb","text_ar":"اَحْزَاب"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, K,) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"parties, classes, bodies, divisions,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) ―         -b2-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He divided"},{"kind":"text","text":"the Kur-án"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"into"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHozaAb","text_ar":"اَحْزَاب"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, Mgh, TA,) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"set portions for particular acts of prayer, &c.;"},{"kind":"text","text":"the doing of which is forbidden. (Mgh.) [But it may also be used as meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He divided"},{"kind":"text","text":"the Kur-án"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"into sixtieth portions."},{"kind":"text","text":"]"}],"source_refs":["A","K","TA","S","Mgh"]},{"entry_id":"n7829","headword_ar":"حَزْبٌ","root":"Hzb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuzaAbapN","text_ar":"حُزَابَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A severe,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distressing, event:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one that straitens,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overcomes,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"suddenly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unexpectedly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n7830","headword_ar":"حِزْبٌ","root":"Hzb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", in its primary acceptation,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A party,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"company of men, assembling themselves on account of an event that has befallen them"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liA^amori Hazabahumo","text_ar":"لِاَمْرِ حَزَبَهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"): (Ksh and Bd in v. 61:) [and then, in a general sense,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an assembly, a collective body,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"company, of men:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, A, Mgh, L, K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a party, portion, division,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"class,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, L, Msb, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of men:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, Msb, TA:) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"troops,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"combined forces, of a man;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his party, partisans,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"faction, prepared,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ready, for fighting and the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"companions,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sect,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party in opinions"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tenets,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a man:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any party agreeing in hearts and actions, whether meeting together or not:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(El-Moajam, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHozaAbN","text_ar":"اَحْزَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, A, Mgh, Msb, L, K.) And the pl., with the article,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Those people who leagued together to wage war against Mohammad:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the parties that combined to war with the prophets."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And in the Kur xl. 31,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The people of Noah and 'Ád and Thamood, and those whom God destroyed after them,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as the people of Pharaoh."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yawomu AlA^aHozaAbi","text_ar":"يَوْمُ الاَحْزَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The day of the combined forces;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the day"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"war"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the moat"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxanodaq","text_ar":"الخَنْدَق"},{"kind":"text","text":"). (Mgh, Msb, TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wirodN","text_ar":"وِرْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, Msb, K, TA,) either in its proper sense,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A turn,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"time, of coming to water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or in the sense next following, which is tropical. (TA.) ―         -b3-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A set portion of the Kur-án,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Mgh, L, TA,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of prayer,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, L, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of which a man imposes upon himself the recital"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Mgh, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"on a particular occasion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at a particular time;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a set portion of prayer,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of recitation"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the Kur-án"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"&c., which a person is accustomed to perform:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) pl. as above. (Mgh.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaraA^a Hizobahu mina AlquroA=ni","text_ar":"قَرَاَ حِزْبَهُ مِنَ القُرْا=نِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He recited his set portion of the Kur-án"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kamo Hizobuka","text_ar":"كَمْ حِزْبُكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"How much is thy set portion"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the Kur-án ?]. (A.) ―         -b4-  [Also (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sixtieth portion of the Kur-án."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b5-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A portion, share,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lot,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA,) of wealth, or property: or perhaps a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jizobN","text_ar":"جِزْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; since IAar says that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HizobN","text_ar":"حِزْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies “ a company of men; ” and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jizobN","text_ar":"جِزْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"“ a portion, share, or lot. ” (TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A weapon,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weapons, of war;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"silaAHN","text_ar":"سِلَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, A, K, TA;) i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=lapN","text_ar":"ا=لَةٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HarobK","text_ar":"حَرْبٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)       -A3-  See also what next follows."}],"source_refs":["IAar","A","Mgh","L","K","S","Msb","TA"]}]}}